Package: rubberDucky
Title: Utilities for Working with DuckDB and MotherDuck
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chris", "Hames", email = "chris@metagen.com.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of utility functions for working with DuckDB and 
    MotherDuck databases. Provides simplified connection handling, connection 
    pooling, and data upload functions with support for spatial data.
